data.description: Welcome to 210 Sussex Aly, a beautiful residence nestled on a generous .31-acre lot, offering the perfect blend of comfort, style, and outdoor living. Ideally situated within walking distance of downtown Millsboro, where a plethora of shops and dining venues await.  As you approach the property, you will notice the added touches that make this home truly special. The privacy fence that envelops the back yard ensures a tranquil retreat, while the extended concrete patio and additional paver patio with bench seating and a firepit provide the ideal setting for outdoor gatherings. Two gazebos grace the landscape—one dedicated to lounging and another for enjoying al fresco dining, creating distinct spaces for relaxation and entertainment. The thoughtful seller add-ons continue with the inclusion of an outdoor utility sink, making outdoor chores a breeze. The addition of a new HVAC system and a vapor barrier in the crawl space contributes to the overall maintenance and efficiency of the home. The glass sliding doors in the dining area seamlessly connect the indoor and outdoor spaces, allowing for an abundance of natural light and easy access to the backyard oasis. Practical updates extend to the structural elements, with a new roof installed in 2020, providing peace of mind and protection for years to come.  Inside, the well-designed floor plan includes gorgeous hardwood floors, crown molding, a living room, dining room, and a kitchen adorned with stainless steel appliances. The primary bedroom boasts an attached bath, offering a private sanctuary within the home. Two additional bedrooms, one featuring a convenient Murphy Bed, provide flexibility for various needs.  Step outside to the expansive backyard, where you'll discover two storage sheds w/electric, perfect for organizing and storing outdoor essentials. Whether you're looking for a quiet retreat or a space to entertain, the outdoor amenities of this property offer endless possibilities.  Experience the best of both indoor and outdoor living at 210 Sussex Aly—a home that combines comfort, convenience, and a touch of outdoor paradise!
